<paragraph id="FAE43EF25C7A8783DEF93D2B69126251" pageId="0" pageNumber="27">Pastures and grasslands along roads, fallow fields, gardens, margins of watercourses and more or less nitrified soils of all types; edaphically indifferent; 0-2100 m a.s.l.</paragraph>
